EN: She takes her work very seriously.
ZH: 3. 他对待失败充满了勇气。
EN: He faces failure with courage.
ZH: 4. 我们应该对待每个人都充满爱心。
EN: We should treat everyone with love.
ZH: 5. 他对待老人很有耐心。
EN: He is very patient with old people.
ZH: 6. 她对待家人非常关心。
EN: She cares deeply for her family.
ZH: 7. 他对待女友很体贴。
EN: He is very considerate towards his girlfriend.
ZH: 8. 她对待动物非常善良。
EN: She is very kind to animals.
ZH: 9. 他对待待人和善。
EN: He deals with people in a friendly manner.
ZH: 10. 我们应该对待每个人都平等。
EN: We should treat everyone equally.
ZH: 11. 他对待朋友的建议非常认真听取。
EN: He listens very carefully to his friends' advice.
ZH: 12. 她对待学习从不马虎。
EN: She never takes her studies lightly.
ZH: 13. 老师应该对待学生公平公正。
EN: Teachers should treat students fairly.
ZH: 14. 他对待人生充满热情。
EN: He approaches life with enthusiasm.
ZH: 15. 她对待工作很尽职尽责。
EN: She is very diligent in her work.
ZH: 16. 他对待艺术有着深深的热爱。
EN: He has a deep passion for art.
ZH: 17. 我们应该对待自然环境更加尊重。
EN: We should treat nature with more respect.
ZH: 18. 他对待义务工作非常乐于助人。
EN: He is very helpful in voluntary work.
ZH: 19. 她对待生活充满了乐观。
EN: She approaches life with optimism.
ZH: 20. 他对待病人非常温柔体贴。
EN: He is very gentle and caring towards patients.
